data.description: Classic style Farmhome with a covered front porch and tons of original character sits on a sprawling lot in the quiet neighborhood of New Windsor.   This 3BR/2BA home is move-in ready featuring hardwood flooring, and updates throughout.  Park in the oversized driveway, make your way to the front door past well kept landscaping, and open the door into your forever home.  Step into a spacious entry hall boasting a pellet stove with a brick firewall, and an open view into the large living room offering tons of natural light.  Walk through into an amazing dining area and kitchen.  The open concept space offers the ideal place to host family events. The kitchen features plenty of colorful cabinets to the ceiling finished with crown moldings, stainless steel appliances, a subway tiled backsplash, and a double stainless sink under a window.  To complete the main living space is a full bath and laundry with storage.  An open, double sided staircase leads to the second floor offering three primary sized bedrooms, and a large walk-in closet off a full bath.  The lower level is unfinished offering storage, utilities, with a walk-out through Bilco doors. From the french doors in the dining room, step out onto a large wood deck that leads to a fenced portion of the sprawling yard offering tons of green space, access to a large driveway, and storage shed.  This home is perfect for any new homeowner with so much to offer including Solar Panels for energy saving opportunities.  Imagine all this and in close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and commuter routes.
